Vehicles.name: Lisbet the Corolla
Vehicles.description:
A 5 door silver automatic Toyota Corolla. This car seats 5 people.

IMPORTANT!

The fuel card in this car only works for E10 or Unleaded 91 petrol. Please only use E10 or Unleaded 91 when refuelling.
